text: Ra jaba tapa'ile yasta manisaharula'i dekhnuhuncha jo hamra ayataharuko barema anargala bakvasa garirakheka chan bhane tiniharubata alaga bha'ihalnus, yahamsam'ma ki tiniharu aru kurama vyasta bha'ihalun. Ra yadi saitanale yo kura tapa'ila'i virsa'idincha bhane yada bha'e pachi aparadhiharuko sathama nabasnus
